+# _glm-agent-0002-schema-assertion-runner-tests - SOP Brainstorming
+
+Ideas and rough drafts for project-specific SOPs before implementation.
+
+## Workflow
+
+```
+docs/brainstorming/SOPs/    →  Ideas, rough analysis (THIS FOLDER)
+         ↓
+docs/sops/                  →  Implemented project SOPs
+```
+
+## Adding Ideas
+
+When you identify a repeated workflow or process:
+
+1. Create a brainstorm file: `YYYY-MM-DD-sop-idea-name.md`
+2. Document:
+   - What problem it solves
+   - Steps involved
+   - Tools/skills needed
+   - Pain points
+3. When ready, implement in `docs/sops/`
+
+## Template for Brainstorm
+
+```markdown
+# SOP Idea: [Name]
+
+**Date**: YYYY-MM-DD
+**Status**: Idea | Exploring | Ready to Implement
+
+## Problem
+What workflow is this trying to standardize?
+
+## Current Pain Points
+- Issue 1
+- Issue 2
+
+## Proposed Solution
+How would an SOP help?
+
+## Steps Identified
+1. Step 1
+2. Step 2
+
+## Tools/Skills Needed
+- Tool 1
+- Skill 1
+
+## Open Questions
+- Question 1?
+```
+
+## Current Ideas
+
+| Idea | Status | Notes |
+|------|--------|-------|
+| (none yet) | | |
+
+## Related
+
+- Implemented SOPs: `docs/sops/`
+- Global SOPs: `~/.claude/skills/sop-*.md`
